# catppuccin mocha — stock Ghostty theme with one deviation, on 7/15.
# Mocha is the inverse of the usual blaze problem: stock puts subtext0 #a6adc8
# on 7 and subtext1 #bac2de on 15, both DIMMER than body fg #cdd6f4 — so
# "bright white" text (Claude Code headers, bold output) renders *fainter* than
# ordinary text. Both slots are pinned to body fg per this repo's convention.
# Everything else is verbatim upstream.
